room_title: Escape room "The Unknown" by Immersion in Marysville
room_description:
A well-respected genetic scientist turned mad. His daughter diagnosed with a terminal illness, and modern medicine failed to provide a cure. He decided to take matters into his own hands. What happened next is unknown.
After reports of disappearances in the area, your team was contacted to investigate. Your team leader has been out of contact for 48 hours and you fear the worst. It is time for you to find him, and discover what is going on. Will you succeed in escaping from the unknown?
